des:
Established in 2018, Mix It Radio, based in Laredo, Texas, was created by Grow Laredo to fill a gap in the local music scene. Recognizing the lack of modern hits on local radio stations, Mix It Radio was born with a mission to deliver the hottest music and top DJs to its listeners. Tune in to hear chart-toppers like Bad Bunny, Drake, and Peso Pluma, all blended with the energy of electronic dance music (EDM). This unique mix of genres has quickly become the soundtrack for those craving a fresh, vibrant vibe on the streets of Laredo.

Discover a new sound with Mix It Radio, where music comes to life.
